java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, JRChangeEventsSupport, JRAlignment, JRBox, JRBoxContainer, JRChild, JRCloneable, JRCommonElement, JRCommonText, JRElement, JRFont, JRPropertiesHolder, JRStaticText, JRStyleContainer, JRTextElement, JRVisitable
public class JRBaseStaticText
extends JRBaseTextElement
implements JRStaticText

This class is used for representing a static text element. Together with its parents, it contains the full functionality needed for handling a static text.
